AngloGold Says Worker Injured at Its Kopanang Mine Two Months Ago Has Died

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-01T07:04:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/anglogold-says-worker-injured-at-its-kopanang-mine-two-months-ago-has-died.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  said a worker
who was injured at its Kopanang mine in  South Africa  two months
ago died in hospital yesterday.  The company commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
